Interface EmsSidc

public interface EmsSidc

SIDC constants for graphics in the "Emergency Management" scheme (MIL-STD-2525C Appendix G). The constants in this interface are "masked" SIDCs. All fields except Scheme, Category, and Function ID are filled with hyphens. (The other fields do not identity a type of graphic, they modify the graphic.)

Note: this interface only defines constants for tactical graphics in Appendix G.
